quran[8]{c,v,t,f}:
  7,74,"Ẹ tún rántí nígbà tí (Allāhu) ṣe yín ní àrólé lẹ́yìn àwọn ara ‘Ād. Ó sì fún yín ní ilé ìgbé lórí ilẹ̀; ẹ̀ ń kọ́ ilé ńláńlá sínú pẹ̀tẹ́lẹ̀, ẹ sì ń gbẹ́ àwọn ilé sínú àpáta. Ẹ rántí àwọn ìdẹ̀ra Allāhu, kí ẹ sì má ṣèbàjẹ́ sórí ilẹ̀.",""
  7,75,"Àwọn àgbààgbà tó ṣègbéraga nínú ìjọ rẹ̀ wí fún àwọn tí wọ́n fojú ọ̀lẹ wò (ìyẹn) àwọn tó gbàgbọ́ lódodo nínú wọn pé: “Ǹjẹ́ ẹ mọ̀ pé dájúdájú Sọ̄lih ni Òjíṣẹ́ láti ọ̀dọ̀ Olúwa rẹ̀?” Wọ́n sọ pé: “Dájúdájú àwa gbàgbọ́ nínú ohun tí wọ́n fi rán an níṣẹ́.”",""
  7,76,"Àwọn tó ṣègbéraga wí pé: “Dájúdájú àwa ṣàì gbàgbọ́ nínú ohun tí ẹ̀yin gbàgbọ́.”",""
  7,77,"Nítorí náà, wọ́n gún abo ràkúnmí náà pa. Wọ́n sì tàpá sí àṣẹ Olúwa wọn. Wọ́n sì wí pé: “Sọ̄lih, mú ohun tí o ṣe ní ìlérí fún wa ṣẹ tí o bá wà nínú àwọn Òjíṣẹ́.”",""
  7,78,"Nítorí náà, ohùn igbe líle tó mi ilẹ̀ tìtì gbá wọn mú. Wọ́n sì di ẹni tó dà lulẹ̀, tí wọ́n ti dòkú sínú ìlú wọn.",""
  7,79,"Nígbà náà, (Sọ̄lih) ṣẹ́rí kúrò lọ́dọ̀ wọn, ó sì sọ pé: “Ẹ̀yin ìjọ mi, mo kúkú ti jẹ́ iṣẹ́ Olúwa mi fún yín. Mo sì ti fún yín ní ìmọ̀ràn rere ṣùgbọ́n ẹ̀yin kò fẹ́ràn àwọn onímọ̀ràn rere.”",""
  7,80,"(Rántí Ànábì) Lūt, nígbà tí ó sọ fún ìjọ rẹ̀ pé: “Ṣé ẹ óò máa ṣe ìbàjẹ́ ni tí kò sí ẹnì kan nínú àwọn ẹ̀dá tó ṣe irú rẹ̀ rí?",""
  7,81,"Dájúdájú ẹ̀yin (ọkùnrin) ń lọ jẹ adùn (ìbálòpọ̀) lára àwọn ọkùnrin (ẹgbẹ́ yín) dípò àwọn obìnrin! Àní sẹ́, ìjọ alákọyọ ni yín.”",""
